{
  "stem": "4830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when they came, this last part of Budapest was evacuated by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They realized that they cannot resist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a strong point that they wanted to use for resistance, which was just the opposite house to us where my father's store was and where my-- where our home was.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this house, with everything in it-- the whole block-- was burned in the last day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they evacuated it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first thing-- we were guarding our house already, so I was on duty and watched as the Germans were leaving at the beginning of the night on the 16th to 17th.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And around 5 o'clock in the morning, the Russians came in through the basements.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see, at the end of the war, you could not go out at all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was such a heavy artillery barrage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we broke from one air raid shelter to another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were built in such a fashion that underground you could move.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they used this place to come in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Were very poorly dressed people, just like the German propaganda showed it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Somebody who had seen them, for example, hugged the first Russian soldier who came and he hugged him back and took his watch.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Just as they said it on their posters-- the Germans-- and, you know, they just came in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Russian soldiers were-- the first front-line soldiers did nothing-- occupied the place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The next wave did a great deal of opening up stores, robbing everything that was in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Not so for themselves, because they distributed it amongst bystanders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were the ones who attacked all the women that were available and raped them, except in our hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
